author: matthew miranda
title: matthew miranda
text: Nengun totally backs up what they offer. I was trying to find a part that is longer carried in the United States. Nengun offers to find you what you are looking for. They sourced the part for my request in a timely fashion. As soon as I sent my PayPal payment, Nengun replied with the shipping details. Part arrived 1 day sooner than scheduled.
